					<a style="color: white; font-size: 20px" href="Login.jsp" title="Login">Login</a>
				</div>
			</h1>
		</div>
		<h1 style="text-align: center">Problems</h1>
		<div style="align: center">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\chart1.png" style="width: 60%;">
							<div class="centered" style="font-size: 50px">23%</div>
						</div>
						23% of nursing home admissions are a result of non-adherence
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\chart2.png" style="width: 60%;">
							<div class="centered" style="font-size: 50px">50%</div>
						</div>
						Less than 50% of prescriptions are taken as prescribed
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\chart3.png" style="width: 60%;">
							<div class="centered" style="font-size: 50px">$213B</div>
						</div>
						Misuse of meds costs US Healthcare System $213 billion annually
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<h1 style="text-align: center">Solution</h1>
		<div style="align: center">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="column" style="width: 45%; padding-top: 0px">
					<div class="card" style="padding-top: 0px">
						<img src="images\calendarbg.jpg" style="width: 100%; height: 100%">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="column" style="width: 45%; padding-top: 0px">
					<div class="card" style="text-align: justify; padding-top: 0px">
						MediTrack enables families and care professionals to remotely
						track medication intake of their loved ones, which helps families
						to alleviate the stress associated with caregiving, and care
						professionals to offer medication reminder services more
						efficiently. Our solution is based on medication packaging, which
						is familiar to most seniors so they do not need any training on
						new technology.</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<h1 style="text-align: center">Features</h1>
		<div style="align: center">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%; overflow: visible">
