						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\reminder (1).png" style="width: 60%;">
						</div>
						<ul style="text-align: left">
							<li>Schedule reminders</li>
							<li>You can select when to remind</li>
							<li>Repeat reminders as you like</li>
							<li>Different types of reminders: sms/IVR</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%; overflow: visible">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\calendar.png" style="width: 60%;">
						</div>
						<ul style="text-align: left">
							<li>Calendar view for easy tracking</li>
							<li>Directly Add/edit reminders from calendar</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="column" style="width: 29%; overflow: visible">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="container">
							<img src="images\prescription (1).png" style="width: 60%;">
						</div>
						<ul style="text-align: left">
							<li>Day view for easy comprehension</li>
							<li>Directly modify from the list</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
